    public abstract class SwInteractionResourceImpl
extends SwResourceImpl
implements SwInteractionResource
    An implementation of the model object 'Sw Interaction Resource'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Is Intra Memory Partition Interaction
    • Waiting Queue Policy
    • Waiting Queue Capacity
    • Waiting Policy Elements
